ng $\\smash{10^{4}}$ sq. deg, such as the $Euclid$ mission and $LSST$,\nwhere the pre-selection of candidates for any kind of SL analysis will be\nindispensable due to the expected enormous data volume.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2018 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-12"}
