rio, ligands with higher\naffinity to their binding sites delay the power laws. Our results can be useful\nfor extracting hidden time scales in experiments where kinetic rates for\nligand-receptor interactions are measured in microchannels, as well as for cell\nsignaling via diffusing molecules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2018 22:41:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-12"}
