 information about the formation of\ndefects in Nb3Sn coatings such as large thin regions, Sn-deficient regions,\nwhich are critical to the performance of Nb3Sn superconducting radiofrequency\ncavities for accelerators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jul 2018 23:07:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 30 Jun 2019 22:09:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
