derstanding conformational flexibility is key to\nprovide an accurate description of the solid/liquid interface during crystal\ndissolution and growth, and therefore its relevance should be systematically\nassessed in the formulation of mesoscopic growth models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2018 03:28:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 09:44:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-13"}
